        "answer": "2",
        "gaokaoConnection": "$\\sin(x+\\pi/2)=\\cos x$，$f(x)=\\sin2x-x^2$，画图看交点个数"
      },
      {
        "id": "func-z4",
        "unitId": "func-zeros",
        "difficulty": 2,
        "type": "fill",
        "prompt": "$f(x)=|2^x-2|-b$有两个零点，$b$范围____。",
        "answer": "$(0,2)$",
        "gaokaoConnection": "画图：$y=|2^x-2|$与$y=b$有两个交点，$0<b<2$"
      },
      {
        "id": "func-z5",
        "unitId": "func-zeros",
        "difficulty": 1,
        "type": "fill",
        "prompt": "$f(x)=x^3-\\dfrac{1}{2^x}$零点区间____",
        "answer": "$(0,1)$",
        "gaokaoConnection": "$f(0)=-1<0,f(1)=1-1/2>0$，零点在$(0,1)$"
      },
      {
        "id": "func-z6",
        "unitId": "func-zeros",
        "difficulty": 2,
        "type": "fill",
        "prompt": "$f(x)=\\ln x-x-\\dfrac{1}{2}$零点个数____",
        "answer": "$2$",
        "gaokaoConnection": "$f(1)=-3/2<0$，$f(e)=1/2-e-1/2=-e<0$？$f'(x)=1/x-1$，$x=1$处最大值$f(1)=-3/2<0$... 需要重新分析"
      },
      {
        "id": "func-z7",
        "unitId": "func-zeros",
        "difficulty": 2,
        "type": "fill",
        "prompt": "$f(x)=(x-1)e^x-a$在$(-2,+\\infty)$恰2个零点，$a$范围____",
        "answer": "$\\left(-\\infty,\\dfrac{1}{e}\\right)$",
        "gaokaoConnection": "$g(x)=(x-1)e^x$在$x=-1$处极小值$-2/e$，$x\\to+\\infty$时$g\\to+\\infty$，$g(0)=-1$"
      }
    ]
  },
  "derivative-concept": {
    "title": "导数的概念与几何意义",
    "exercises": [
      {
        "id": "deriv-c1",
        "unitId": "derivative-concept",
        "difficulty": 1,
        "type": "fill",
        "prompt": "$y=\\dfrac{1}{3}x^3+1$在$(-3,-8)$切线斜率____",
        "answer": "$9$",
        "gaokaoConnection": "$y'=x^2$，在$x=-3$处$y'=9$"
      },
      {
        "id": "deriv-c2",
        "unitId": "derivative-concept",
        "difficulty": 2,
        "type": "fill",
        "prompt": "$y=e^x+x+a$切线为$y=2x+5$，则$a=$____。",
        "answer": "3",
        "gaokaoConnection": "切线斜率$y'=e^x+1=2$得$x=0$，切点$(0,1+a)$在切线上"
      },
      {
        "id": "deriv-c3",
        "unitId": "derivative-concept",
        "difficulty": 2,
        "type": "fill",
        "prompt": "$y=x\\ln x$与$y=kx-2$相切，则$k=$____。",
        "answer": "$1+\\ln2$",
        "gaokaoConnection": "设切点$(x_0,x_0\\ln x_0)$，$y'=\\ln x+1=k$，且$kx_0-2=x_0\\ln x_0$"
      },
      {
        "id": "deriv-c4",
        "unitId": "derivative-concept",
        "difficulty": 2,
        "type": "fill",
        "prompt": "$f(x)=x^3-x,g(x)=x^2+a$，$x_1=-1$处公切线，$a=$____。",
        "answer": "$\\dfrac{5}{4}$",
        "gaokaoConnection": "$f'(-1)=g'(-1)$且切线方程相同，求出切线后再求$g(x)$的$a$"
      },
      {
        "id": "deriv-c5",
        "unitId": "derivative-concept",
        "difficulty": 2,
        "type": "fill",
        "prompt": "$f(x)=x^3+ax+\\dfrac{1}{4}$，x轴为切线，求$a$。",
        "answer": "$-1$",
        "gaokaoConnection": "切线$y=0$，$f(x_0)=0, f'(x_0)=0$，$3x_0^2+a=0$且$x_0^3+ax_0=-1/4$"
      },
      {
        "id": "deriv-c6",
        "unitId": "derivative-concept",
        "difficulty": 2,
        "type": "fill",
        "prompt": "$y=x+ae^x$存在两条过原点切线，$a$范围______。",
        "answer": "$(0,+\\infty)$",
        "gaokaoConnection": "切线过原点：$y'=e^x+ae^x=(1+a)e^x$，切线$y=(1+a)e^{x_0}(x-x_0)+x_0+ae^{x_0}$过$(0,0)$"
      },
      {
        "id": "deriv-c7",
        "unitId": "derivative-concept",
        "difficulty": 2,
        "type": "fill",
        "prompt": "$f(x)=\\dfrac{e^x+2\\sin x}{1+x^2}$在$(0,1)$切线与坐标轴围成三角形面积____",
        "answer": "$\\dfrac{1}{6}$",
        "gaokaoConnection": "$f(0)=1,f'(0)=1$，切线$y=x+1$，与$x$轴交$(-1,0)$，与$y$轴交$(0,1)$，$S=1/2$"
      }
    ]
  },
  "derivative-monotonicity": {
    "title": "导数与函数单调性",
    "exercises": [
      {
        "id": "deriv-m1",
        "unitId": "derivative-monotonicity",
        "difficulty": 2,
        "type": "solve",
        "prompt": "$f(x)=ae^x-x$，讨论单调性。",
        "answer": "$a\\le0$时$f(x)$在$\\mathbf{R}$递减；$a>0$时$f(x)$在$(-\\infty,-\\ln a)$递减，在$(-\\ln a,+\\infty)$递增",
        "gaokaoConnection": "$f'(x)=ae^x-1$，按$a\\le0$和$a>0$分类讨论"
      },
      {
        "id": "deriv-m2",
        "unitId": "derivative-monotonicity",
        "difficulty": 2,
        "type": "solve",
        "prompt": "$f(x)=ae^{2x}+(a-2)e^x-x$，讨论单调性。",
        "answer": "$a\\le0$时递减；$0<a<2$时在$(-\\infty,\\ln\\frac{2-a}{2a})$递减；$a\\ge2$时在$\\mathbf{R}$递增",
        "gaokaoConnection": "$f'(x)=(2e^x+1)(ae^x-1)$，令$f'(x)=0$得$e^x=1/a$"
      },
      {
        "id": "deriv-m3",
        "unitId": "derivative-monotonicity",
        "difficulty": 2,
        "type": "solve",
        "prompt": "$f(x)=\\dfrac{1}{x}-x+a\\ln x$，讨论单调性。",
        "answer": "$a\\le2$时在$(0,+\\infty)$递减；$a>2$时在$(0,\\frac{a-\\sqrt{a^2-4}}{2})$和$(\\frac{a+\\sqrt{a^2-4}}{2},+\\infty)$递减，中间递增",
        "gaokaoConnection": "$f'(x)=-\\dfrac{1}{x^2}-1+\\dfrac{a}{x}=\\dfrac{-x^2+ax-1}{x^2}$，分析分子判别式"
      }
    ]
  },
  "derivative-extremum": {
    "title": "极值与最值",
    "exercises": [
      {
        "id": "deriv-e1",
        "unitId": "derivative-extremum",
        "difficulty": 2,
        "type": "solve",
        "prompt": "$a=2,f(x)=x^a-a^x(x>0)$，求单调区间。",
        "answer": "$f(x)$在$(0,2)$递增，在$(2,+\\infty)$递减",
        "gaokaoConnection": "$f'(x)=2x-2^x\\ln2$，分析$2x$与$2^x\\ln2$的大小关系"
      },
      {
        "id": "deriv-e2",
        "unitId": "derivative-extremum",
        "difficulty": 2,
        "type": "solve",
        "prompt": "$a=-2,f(x)=(1-ax)\\ln(1+x)-x$，求极值。",
        "answer": "$f(x)$在$x=0$处取极大值0，无极小值",
        "gaokaoConnection": "$f'(x)=(1+2x)\\cdot\\dfrac{1}{1+x}+2\\ln(1+x)-1$，化简后分析符号"
      }
    ]
  },
