        "unitId": "derivative-always",
        "difficulty": 2,
        "type": "fill",
        "prompt": "$f(x)=ae^x-\\ln x$在$(1,2)$递增，$a$最小值____",
        "answer": "$e^{-1}$",
        "gaokaoConnection": "$f'(x)=ae^x-\\dfrac{1}{x}\\ge0$在$(1,2)$恒成立，$a\\ge\\dfrac{1}{xe^x}$的最大值"
      },
      {
        "id": "deriv-a3",
        "unitId": "derivative-always",
        "difficulty": 3,
        "type": "fill",
        "prompt": "$f(x)=\\begin{cases}x^2+2x+a-2,&x\\le0\\\\-x^2+2x-2a,&x>0\\end{cases}$，$\\forall x\\ge-3,f(x)\\le|x|$，$a$范围____。",
        "answer": "$\\left[\\dfrac{1}{2},+\\infty\\right)$",
        "gaokaoConnection": "分段讨论$x\\le0$和$x>0$时$f(x)\\le|x|$恒成立的条件"
      }
    ]
  },
  "derivative-zeros": {
    "title": "导数与零点",
    "exercises": [
      {
        "id": "deriv-z1",
        "unitId": "derivative-zeros",
        "difficulty": 3,
        "type": "solve",
        "prompt": "$f(x)=\\dfrac{ax^2+x-1}{e^x}$\n(1)求$(0,-1)$切线；\n(2)$a\\ge1$，证明$f(x)+e\\ge0$。",
        "answer": "(1) $y=x-1$\n(2) 求$f(x)$最小值，证明$f_{\\min}\\ge-e$",
