        "answer": "(1) $a\\le0$递增；$a>0$时在$(-\\infty,\\ln a)$递减，$(\\ln a,+\\infty)$递增\n(2) $a\\le e-1$",
        "gaokaoConnection": "分离参数：$a\\le\\dfrac{e^x-x^2-1}{x}$，求右边最小值"
      }
    ]
  },
